{"tid":1669323,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(突發) 區議員義工要人！係你啦同學！","createTime":"2019-10-22T13:13:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-23T04:49:19.000Z","uid":123183,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"844369ef60a79d7025bf1c1bb6d3822a70ff1bb8","tid":1669323,"uid":123183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T13:13:14.000Z","msg":"辛苦各位手足呢段時間付出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />身為和理非鍵戰backup嘅大家又係時候到你地出場！尤其學生嘅大家更加可以幫手做區議員義工！但記得最好幾個一齊報名小心安全！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n//學生歷量全力支持民主派參選人<br />\n<br />\n區議會是香港地區層次的議會，就市民日常生活事務向政府提供意見。<br />\n<br />\n學生歷量在此招募學生義工為各區民主派候選人助選。助選工作非常簡單，包括派傳單、叫口號、舉宣傳牌等。希望大家踴躍幫忙🙏🏻<br />\n<br />\n義工申請表:<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSen3iY07zRM37Co8C4EjywqaBBudgA7MWU48kRexeoQnH3gYw/viewform\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fforms%2Fd%2Fe%2F1FAIpQLSen3iY07zRM37Co8C4EjywqaBBudgA7MWU48kRexeoQnH3gYw%2Fviewform&d=tlSH0trWbW1MAbtCTa3DU1YPZSwMlx1ag7qd%2FaAfmLs%3D&h=3c725ae1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSen3iY07zRM37Co8C4EjywqaBBudgA7MWU48kRexeoQnH3gYw/viewform</a> //<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6VtAzcg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6VtAzcg.jpg&h=c1e42e40&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e0e16f7893c2960714de35290f98ba20abb59597","tid":1669323,"uid":164435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T13:17:45.000Z","msg":"now區選情報Telegram Channel <a href=\"https://t.me/nowpolitics_dc2019\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fnowpolitics_dc2019&d=tlSH0trWbW1MAbtCTa3DU1YPZSwMlx1ag7qd%2FaAfmLs%3D&h=69ac9eac\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/nowpolitics_dc2019</a>"},{"pid":"ce5933420b3f2880b4a83561244a876054154cf1","tid":1669323,"uid":14897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T13:28:15.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif